        {
            "name": "Anancus",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "The anancus is an ancient species of elephant with unusually long tusks and a trunk shorter than its more modern cousins.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Animal</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Nature</a></u>)</b>: DC 24",
